Package gov.nih.nlm.nls.lvg.Util Description

Contains LVG general utility classes of comparators, Bit operations, Case, In, Out, Strip operations, token operation, Char, Str, and Word. This package serves as an utility package for Lexical Tools. It is not intended to be used by the end users directly. End users may skip this package.
Since:
2002
